STATE EX REL. GALLUZZO
v.
WEITHMAN 2018-1228 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018 O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, FRENCH, FISCHER, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION
